Dataset Name: "Oil, Gas, Electricity, Global industrial production"

Description: "Data regarding Oil, Gas, Electricity, Global industrial production."

Keywords: "Oil, Gas, Electricity, Industrial production"

Version: "N/A"

Date Created: "2023-11-30"

Last Updated: "2023-11-30"

Updated by: "Robet-Adrian Grecu"

Source: https://www.bloomberg.com/europe (Bloomberg - for oil and gas price, both daily and monthly)
https://www.opcom.ro/acasa/ro (OPCOM - for electricity transaction prices)
https://www.eia.gov/international/data/world/petroleum-and-other-liquids/monthly-petroleum-and-other-liquids-production?pd=5&p=0000000000000000000000000000000000vg&u=0&f=M&v=mapbubble&a=-&i=none&vo=value&t=C&g=00000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000001&l=249-ruvvvvvfvtvnvv1vrvvvvfvvvvvvfvvvou20evvvvvvvvvvnvvvs0008&s=94694400000&e=1682899200000
(US Energy Information Administration - for oil prodution)
https://databank.worldbank.org/reports.aspx?source=1179&series=IPTOTSAKD# (World Bank - for global industrial production)

Code: N/A"

Data frequency: "Monthly - for all indicators", "Daily - for oil and gas prices" 

Timeframe: Daily indicators "2010-1-4 : 2023-10-13"
Monthly indicators: "2010-1-1 : 2023-4-1"

Features: "
Data: Date of the recorded observation in format dd.mm.aaaa
BRENT_OIL - daily data - close price of the day, USD per Barrel
BRENT_OIL - monthly data - close price of the last day of the month, USD per Barrel
EU Natural Gas - daily data - close price of the day, EUR/MWh
EU Natural Gas - monthly data - close price of the last day of the month, EUR/MWh
Oil production - monthly data - global oil production annual percentage change (change based on the same month of the previous year) 
Global Industrial Production - monthly data - global insutrial production annual percentage change (change based on the same month of the previous year) 
Electricity transaction price - monthly data - monthly average of the electricity transaction price in Romania, lei/MWh

Format: "CSV"

Usage Rights: "Open source, free to use."

Possible Uses: "Determining the link between the energy market and the capital market"

Contact: "N/A"

Additional Resources: N/A"

